      <title>罗杰斯向养老金支持的黑石基金出售50亿美元的网络股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/rogers-sells-5-billion-network-stake-to-pension-backed-blackstone-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗杰斯通讯公司（Rogers Communications Inc.）同意将其无线网络中的股份出售给由黑石公司（Blackstone Inc.）管理的资金，该资金在70亿加元（49亿加元）的股权交易中得到了四项加拿大养老金的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/rogers-sells-5-billion-network-stake-to-pension-backed-blackstone-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:33:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
