      <title>贸易战争掩盖了固体工作数据，美国国债激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/treasuries-hold-4-line-as-jobs-report-powell-speech-loom-large</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贸易商提高了对美联储利率削减的赌注，随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税的影响，美国国债又增加了一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/treasuries-hold-4-line-as-jobs-report-powell-speech-loom-large</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧佩克供应提升，关税动荡的油降至四年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克+出人意料的产量增加以及全球贸易战的惊人产量增加之后，石油跌至四年低点，这也使商品市场从金属到天然气都震撼了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克100号将其抛售从记录扩展到20％：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票在全球范围内跌落，债券飙升，石油跌至四年的低位，中国加强了与唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战的斗争，以加剧对经济放缓的担忧，尽管迹象表现出了坚实的就业市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税颠覆全球增长时，Dollar会在Trump集会后删除</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-wipes-out-post-trump-rally-as-tariffs-upend-global-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）于11月赢得总统职位以来，他的积极关税使全球市场赢得了总统职位，这笔钱已经消除了所有收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-wipes-out-post-trump-rally-as-tariffs-upend-global-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 20:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
